text.tspan: You are banned.

the conclusion that you should be banned.

kicked at least 3 times throughout your time
on this project.
If you were kicked 3 times, you are temporarily
banned. 6 times, a longer temporary ban.
9 times, a permanent ban.
If you have a permanent ban and want to make
an appeal, consult @kieranblackley with
